20dollar%20or%20two%2C%20gig%20workers%20said%20the%20gap%20can%20add%20up%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20many%20have%20seen%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-instacart-gig-workers-saw-earnings-fall-2024-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epay%20decrease%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Uber%20driver%20in%20Massachusetts%20said%20he%20started%20receiving%20duplicative%20offers%20over%20the%20past%20month%20and%20accepted%20some%2C%20though%20the%20payout%20was%20lower%20and%20the%20map%20showed%20it%20was%20the%20same%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20double%20offers%20didn't%20happen%20on%20every%20trip%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20none%20offered%20to%20pay%20him%20more%20the%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20hit%20'match%2C'%20and%20then%20it%20would%20say%20that%20the%20trip%20was%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20driver%20said.%20%26quot%3BShortly%20thereafter%2C%20I'd%20get%20an%20exclusive%20offer%20with%20a%20lower%20price%20for%20the%20same%20trip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESergio%20Avedian%2C%20an%20Uber%20driver%20and%20senior%20contributor%20to%20the%20gig-driver-advocacy%20blog%20and%20YouTube%20channel%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherideshareguy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Rideshare%20Guy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20Uber%20often%20serves%20drivers%20offers%20through%20Trip%20Radar%20as%20they%20are%20finishing%20up%20a%20ride.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20app%20gives%20drivers%2010%20seconds%20to%20accept%20the%20trip%20or%20lose%20it%2C%20meaning%20drivers%20don't%20always%20have%20time%20to%20evaluate%20the%20offer%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKansal's%20response%20on%20X%20represents%20a%20rare%20instance%20in%20which%20Uber's%20C-suite%20publicly%20acknowledged%20a%20problem%20to%20a%20driver%2C%20Avedian%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadding%20that%20the%20user%20tagged%20some