22%3A%22Don't%20throw%20out%20your%20sweatpants.%20Remote%20work%20could%20grow%20as%20younger%20CEOs%20take%20over.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20group%20of%20remote%20coworkers%20get%20together%20for%20a%20once-q-quarter%20in-person%20retreat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f8b5fe1ba468a96ac1168%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwenty-nine-year-old%20startup%20CEO%20Max%20Albert%2C%20center%2C%20poses%20with%20some%20of%20his%20firm's%20remote%20employees%20during%20one%20of%20their%20recent%20quarterly%20in-person%20company%20retreats.%3Cp%3EMax%20Albert%2FAdrenaline%20Interactive%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20big%20employers%20now%20mandate%20full-time%20office%20work%2C%20while%20others%20have%20stuck%20with%20hybrid%20or%20remote%20set-ups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20older%20office-first%20leaders%20retire%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-embracing-remote-work-amid-rto-push-2025-11%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremote%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20expand%2C%20a%20new%20report%20suggests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20younger%20the%20company%20and%20the%20CEO%2C%20the%20better%20your%20chances%20of%20working%20from%20home%2C%20it%20finds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20write%20off%20remote%20work%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-return-to-office-mandate-5-days-week-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-5-days-office-return-mandate-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAT%26amp%3BT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-columbus-ohio-polaris-first-week-rto-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20mandate%20five-day%20office%20returns%2C%20work-from-home%20setups%20are%20poised%20to%20grow%2C%20a%20new%20study%20released%20by%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20show%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fextra-births-align-with-work-from-home-stanford-study-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20work%20remotely%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20often%20when%20employed%20at%20firms%20founded%20after%202015%20than%20at%20those%20founded%20before%201990%20%E2%80%94%20and%20at%20firms%20led%20by%20CEOs%20under%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20future%20generations%20of%20workers%20could%20have%20greater%20flexibility%2C%20said%20Jose%20Maria%20Barrero%2C%20one%20of%20the%20researchers%20behind%20the%20study.%20Leading%20remote%20work%20expert%20Nick%20Bloom%20was%20also%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20older%20companies%20die%20and%20new%20companies%20start%20up%2C%20and%20as%20older%20senior%20executives%20start%20retiring%20and%20they%20get%20replaced%20by%20younger%20ones%2C%20that%20should%20make%20more%20of%20the%20labor%20force%20be%20in%20these%20remote%20work-friendly%20firms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barrero%2C%20who%20is%20a%20finance%20professor%20at%20the%20Autonomous%20Technological%20Institute%20of%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20takeaway%20from%20the%20study%20applies%20to%20the%20present%3A%20The%20younger%20the%20company%20and%20the%20younger%20the%20CEO%2C%20the%20better%20an%20employee's%20chances%20of%20working%20in%20sweatpants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20very%20important%20for%20you%20to%20have%20this%20sort%20of%20flexibility%2C%20you%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20that%20if%20you%20look%20for%20jobs%20at%20young%20firms%20with%20young%20CEOs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barrero.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20jobs%20at%20established%20firms%20with%20young%20CEOs%2C%20though%20it's%20more%20common%20for%20young%20firms%20to%20have%20young%20CEOs%20than%20for%20established%20firms%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df2ecba6-39df-46e6-a256-36c2960c3f13%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20generational%20divide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20that%20Barrero%20co-authored%20is%20based%20on%20monthly%20surveys%20of%208%2C000%20US%20residents%20ages%2020-64%20taken%20throughout%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20finds%20that%20startups%20less%20than%20a%20decade%20old%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20allow%20hybrid%20or%20fully%20remote%20work%2C%20in%20part%20because%20the%20technology%20required%20to%20support%20such%20arrangements%20was%20readily%20available%20when%20they%20were%20founded.%20Many%20companies%20that%20launched%20around%202020%20also%20began%20operating%20remotely%20out%20of%20necessity%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20organizational%20culture%2C%20the%20way%20they%20interact%2C%20the%20way%20they%20set%20up%20their%20workflows%2C%20is%20going%20to%20be%20suited%20to%20a%20much%20more%20work-from-home-friendly%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barrero.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlder%20firms%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20often%20face%20higher%20costs%20when%20changing%20long-standing%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20a%20conglomerate%20that%20has%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20with%20people%20going%20to%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barrero.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20organizational%20culture%20is%20built%20around%20being%20in%20the%20office%20physically%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20seated%20with%20a%20computer%20on%20her%20lap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f8e3dd3c7faef0ece4a62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGeorgia%20Oliver%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20all-remote%20marketing%20firm%20Paper%20Planes%2C%20said%20she%20used%20to%20have%20a%20three-hour%20daily%20commute.%3Cp%3EPaper%20Planes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-nine-year-old%20Georgia%20Oliver%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20all-remote%20marketing%20firm%20Paper%20Planes%2C%20used%20to%20have%20a%20three-hour%20daily%20commute%20while%20working%20in%20corporate%20strategy%20at%20Amazon%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20resented%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20ended%20up%20doing%20less%20work%20than%20I%20would%20at%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20viewing%20the%20matter%20from%20an%20employer's%20perspective%2C%20Oliver%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20in-office%20mandates%20limit%20hiring%20options%20and%20opportunities%20to%20serve%20clients%20in%20a%20range%20of%20markets.%20Paper%20Plane's%2012-person%20staff%20is%20spread%20across%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20measure%20contribution%20through%20delivery%20and%20results%2C%20not%20hours%20at%20a%20desk%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Oliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229dac303e-8592-42e7-8c7d-cda49dccfe0a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'It's%20just%20what%20I'm%20used%20to'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20not%20all%20older%20CEOs%20are%20opposed%20to%20remote%20work.%20Young%20company%20leaders%20may%20be%20more%20inclined%20to%20embrace%20it%2C%20since%20they've%20logged%20fewer%20years%20in%20office-first%20environments%2C%20said%20Barrero.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20Albert%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20an%20all-remote%20startup%2C%20can%20relate.%20Before%20launching%20Adrenaline%20Interactive%2C%20an%20ad%20tech%20company%2C%20in%202024%2C%20he%20briefly%20worked%20in%20an%20office%20from%209-to-5%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20for%20Ford%20Motor.%20Then%20the%20pandemic%20set%20in.%20He's%20been%20remote%20%E2%80%94%20and%20on%20a%20flexible%20schedule%20%E2%80%94%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20what%20I'm%20used%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20trouble%20sitting%20at%20a%20desk%20for%20eight%20hours%20straight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlbert%20said%20he%20does%20see%20value%20in%20teams%20spending%20time%20together%20to%20build%20camaraderie.%20That's%20why%20he%20and%20his%20six%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20who%20live%20in%20Texas%2C%20Illinois%2C%20Florida%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Alabama%2C%20and%20Michigan%20%E2%80%94%20get%20together%20once%20a%20quarter%20for%20a%20company%20retreat%2C%20mixing%20work%20and%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20an%20adventure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Albert%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20a%20permanent%20address%20and%20lives%20out%20of%20Airbnb%20rentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224796afd6-9fd3-4ac1-b89b-5d32df9d6739%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%20isn't%20the%20only%20factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies'%20and%20CEOs'%20ages%20aren't%20the%20only%20factors%20shaping%20employers'%20likelihood%20of%20supporting%20remote%20work%2C%20the%20study%20released%20by%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%20shows.%20Jobs%20that%20can%20be%20done%20entirely%20online%20%E2%80%94%20common%20in%20professional%20services%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20tech%20%E2%80%94%20are%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20remote%2C%20Barrero%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20exceptions.%20Some%20employers%20require%20everyone%20on-site%2C%20even%20when%20only%20certain%20roles%20require%20a%20physical%20presence.%20Barrero%20said%20they%20likely%20do%20this%20to%20avoid%20perceptions%20of%20special%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20though%2C%20the%20data%20collected%20from%20the%20study%20shows%20age%20is%20a%20significant%20factor.%20Employees%20work%20from%20home%20at%20younger%20firms%20almost%20twice%20as%20often%20as%20at%20established%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecent%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20same%20group%20of%20researchers%20showed%20work-from-home%20rates%20were%20only%20declining%20very%20gradually%20between%202023%20and%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barrero.%20%26quot%3BThis%20new%20study%20suggests%20that%20in%20five%20or%2010%20years%2C%20they%20may%20start%20to%20rise%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-younger-ceos-more-likely-to-embrace-remote-work-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771065061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f8b5fe1ba468a96ac1168%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-younger-ceos-more-likely-to-embrace-remote-work-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20study%20suggests%20that%20remote%20work%20could%20grow%20as%20leaders%20who%20rose%20through%20five-day-a-week%20office%20cultures%20give%20way%20to%20a%20younger%20generation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sneedleman%40businessinsider.com%20(Sarah%20E.%20Needleman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-younger-ceos-more-likely-to-embrace-remote-work-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spotify%20CEO%20says%20its%20top%20developers%20'have%20not%20written%20a%20single%20line%20of%20code'%20in%202026%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223521%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spotify%20logo%20with%20a%20shadow%20of%20a%20man%20next%20to%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6825e21cc6ad288d14810177%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222206%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpotify%20removed%20podcasts%20that%20promoted%20the%20sale%20of%20opioids%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESpotify's%20CEO%20says%20the%20company's%20best%20developers%20are%20exclusively%20using%20AI%20to%20w