ashioned%20game%20night.%20Another%20day%2C%20we%20weaved%20between%20tourists%20around%20the%20Museum%20of%20Modern%20Art%2C%20holding%20hands%20as%20we%20studied%20paintings.%20I%20left%20him%20love%20notes%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-turned-garage-into-apartment-for-daughter-to-save-money-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eour%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20dog-shaped%20sticky%20notes%2C%20a%20habit%20from%20early%20in%20our%20relationship%20I'd%20fallen%20out%20of%20as%20life%20got%20busy.%20It%20made%20my%20day%20when%20he%20told%20me%20he%20loved%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a30924a-fa1e-4467-b70b-8ace6de41190%5C%22%3EThe%20wonderful%20world%20of%20whimsy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIncorporating%20whimsy%20into%20my%20life%20has%20been%20the%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%20I%20didn't%20know%20I%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20change%20everything%3B%20I%20still%20ache%20for%20my%20mom%2C%20and%20have%20bouts%20of%20despair%20when%20I%20read%20scary%20headlines.%20Still%2C%20prioritizing%20simple%20joys%20has%20offered%20a%20liferaft%20when%20the%20currents%20threatened%20to%20pull%20me%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20I%20started%20thinking%20about%20%3Cem%3Emyself%20%3C%2Fem%3Eless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227997%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samantha%20G.%20Pettyjohn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698dffbbe1ba468a96abeefc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhimsy%20made%20me%20feel%20the%20magic%20I'd%20been%20missing.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Lombard%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20checked%20out%20a%20book%20at%20the%20library%2C%20my%20brief%20interaction%20with%20my%20librarian%20and%20seeing%20other%20patrons%20absorbed%20in%20reading%20were%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20wrote%20letters%20to%20loved%20ones%2C%20some%20of%20the%