0norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20my%20biggest%20motivation%20is%20building%20something%20from%20scratch%20on%20my%20own%20instead%20of%20within%20a%20big%20company%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-transforming-workplace-faster-than-internet-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epace%20of%20AI%20adoption%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20this%20a%20rare%20window%20to%20do%20something%20new.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20right%20moment%20to%20make%20the%20jump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJoe%20Luchs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(38%2C%20lives%20in%20New%20York%20City)%3A%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20point%20in%20life%20when%20you%20have%20this%20combination%20of%20experience%20plus%20energy%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20very%20good%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-a-business-according-to-successful-entrepreneurs-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estart%20a%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20my%20fifth%20startup%20I've%20worked%20at%2C%20and%20I'm%20still%20young%20enough%20to%20put%20in%20an%2080-hour%20week%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20that%20combination%20is%20good%20for%20starting%20a%20company.%20%3Cem%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20He%20said%20he's%20had%20two%20successful%20exits%20%E2%80%94%20BlueKai%20and%20Beeswax)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20when%20you%20looked%20at%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-companies-startups-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eamazing%20AI%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20what%20they're%20capable%20of%2C%20it%20started%20to%20become%20very%20clear%20that%20this%20tech%20was%20game-changing.%20Despite%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20had%20great%20opportunities%20at%20Amazon%2C%20the%20FOMO%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20get%20in%20on%20this%20AI%20opportunity%20was%20another%20driver%20to%20make%20me%20want%20to%20move%20fast%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%