2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22edc782e0-a9e1-4037-813f-307195d705fe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20get%20comfortable%20leaving%20from%20a%20financial%20perspective%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFerragonio%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20think%20I'm%20in%20a%20good%20place%20financially%20because%20of%20the%20opportunities%20I've%20had%20both%20at%20Amazon%20and%20before%20to%20take%20this%20leap.%20However%2C%20since%20this%20is%20my%20first%20startup%2C%20it%20was%20definitely%20something%20I%20contemplated%20for%20a%20bit.%20That's%20why%20I%20was%20really%20focused%20on%20getting%20feedback%20from%20prospective%20customers%20and%20making%20sure%20we%20had%20a%20product%20we%20had%20a%20clear%20vision%20for%20before%20I%20left%20Amazon.%20As%20of%202026%2C%20we%20both%20now%20have%20a%20small%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuchs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20think%20if%20you%20want%20to%20accrue%20the%20benefits%20of%20what%20startups%20can%20afford%20you%2C%20you%20often%20have%20to%20make%20some%20sacrifices%2C%20including%20short-term%20compensation.%20However%2C%20you'll%20never%20learn%20faster%20than%20you%20will%20in%20a%20startup%20environment%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20worth%20its%20weight%20in%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20folks%20that%20may%20have%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20safety%20in%20Big%20Tech%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20that's%20not%20necessarily%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229251d592-b331-447b-9fd3-5cce8f538928%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20been%20the%20hardest%20part%20of%20starting%20the%20company%20so%20far%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFerragonio%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20say%20getting%20the%20operations%20up%20and%20running%20is%20one%20challenge%2C%20including%20things%20like%20health%20insurance%2C%20accounting%2C%20taxes%2C%20and%20incorporation.%20We're%20currently%20a%20team%20of%20four%20cofounders%20and%20two%20founding%20engineers%2C%20and%20we're%20actively%20hiring%20additional%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20there's%20the%20challenge%20of%20balancing%20customer%20feedback%20in%20the%20early%20days.%20We've%20talked%20to%20hundreds%20of%20potential%20customers%2C%20and%20while%20you%20start%20to%20get%20very%20clear%20signals%20about%20what%20they%20say%20they%20want%2C%20until%20customers%20are%20actually%20using%20the%20product%2C%20you%20don't%20really%20know%20what%20works.%20The%20feedback%20changes%20from%20%26quot%3Bhere's%20a%20mountain%20of%20things%20that%20you%20could%20build%26quot%3B%20to%20what%20you%20should%20build%20to%20truly%20solve%20their%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20balancing%20getting%20enough%20features%20to%20get%20customers%20excited%20without%20overbuilding%20is%20a%20delicate%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1129359-8fb6-4067-b506-6fc39996103b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20advice%20would%20you%20give%20others%20considering%20leaving%20their%20jobs%20to%20start%20something%20new%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFerragonio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Don't%20wait%20for%20the%20perfect%20time.%20There's%20rarely%20a%20perfect%20moment%20to%20leave%20your%20job%2C%20and%20there's%20always%20a%20reason%20to%20stay%2C%20especially%20in%20Big%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20also%20recommend%20talking%20to%20as%20many%20people%20as%20you%20can%20%E2%80%94%20friends%2C%20stakeholders%2C%20potential%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20to%20help%20strengthen%20your%20conviction%20in%20your%20business%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuchs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20think%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20barriers%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20entrepreneurs%20is%20that%20they%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20do%20things%20like%20incorporate%20a%20company%20or%20get%20p