nd%20out%20with%20younger%20diners.%20The%20Mexican%20chain's%20parent%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyum-brands-earnings-trends-gen-z-tastes-taco-bell-kfc-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYum!%20Brands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reported%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20Taco%20Bell%20delivered%207%25%20same-store%20sales%20growth%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20fueled%20in%20part%20by%20transaction%20gains%20that%20skewed%20especially%20strong%20among%20younger%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Sean%20Tresvant%20says%20that%20the%2063-year-old%20brand's%20youthful%20appeal%20is%20deliberate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20brand%20within%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20we%20understand%20where%20culture%20is%2C%20not%20only%20where%20it%20is%2C%20but%20where%20it's%20moving%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Tresvant%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20we%20stay%20really%2C%20really%20relevant%20with%20Gen%20Z%2C%20not%20only%20today%2C%20but%20where%20they're%20moving%20to%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20cultural%20fluency%20shows%20up%20in%20everything%20from%20limited-time%20menu%20drops%20to%20brand%20collaborations.%20Taco%20Bell%20recently%20revived%20fan-favorite%20items%20like%20the%20Quesarito%2C%20launched%20new%20sauce%20collaborations%20and%20a%20viral%20Baja%20Blast%20pie%2C%20and%20has%20leaned%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrand-crossovers-everywhere-tecovas-chilis-chipotle-urban-outfitters-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuzzy%20partnerships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20Y2K-themed%20collaboration%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20Hollister%20that%20sold%20out%20late%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20Yum!%20Brands'%20four%20subsidiaries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20KFC%2C%20Pizza%20Hut%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhabit-burger-ceo-daily-routine-oura-ring-workouts-preserve-energy-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHabit%20Burger%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Taco%20Bell%20is%20the%20primary%20driver%20of%20growth.%20The%20location%20intelligence%20firm%20Placer.ai%20reports%20that%20Taco%20Bell%20delivered%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20consistent%20year-over-year%20monthly%20overall%20visit%20and%20same-store%20visit%20growth%20throughout%20Q4%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaco%20Bell%20also%20consistently%20scores%20well%20on%20the%20InMarket%20Fidelity%20Index%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20ratio%20of%20visits%20to%20a%20chain%20relative%20to%20its%20number%20of%20locations%2C%20highlighting%20a%20brand's%20efficiency%20and%20consumer%20loyalty%20over%20time.%20In%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20ranked%20fifth%20among%20all%20quick-service%20restaurants%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoutperforming%20other%20chains%20among%20consumers%20earning%20less%20than%20%24150%2C000%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esignalling%20broad%20popularity%20among%20fans%20regardless%20of%20income%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETresvant%20argues%20the%20brand's%20resonance%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-dining-trends-communal-table-restaurants-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20particular%20isn't%20just%20about%20marketing%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20execution%20across%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20being%20a%20buzzy%20brand%2C%20you%20look%20at%20value%2C%20you%20look%20at%20digital%2C%20you%20look%20at%20category%20entry%20points%20and%20innovation%2C%20and%20all%20those%20things%20are%20working%20in%20concert%20with%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Tresvant%20said.%20%26quot%3BOther%20brands%20can%20do%20one%20or%20two.%20When%20we%20do%20it%2C%20we%20get%20all%20four%20right%2C%20and%20we're%20very%20good%20in%20each%20part%20of%20that%20magic%20formula.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f7e2258-2b9a-4420-8864-6d78f149e875%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinning%20Gen%20Z%20means%20playing%20by%20different%20rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20engagement%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20become%20a%20major%20driver.%20Tresvant%20said%20active%20loyalty%20members%20climbed%2031%25%20in%202025%2C%20while%20digital%20channels%20saw%20double-digit%20growth%2C%20as%20app-exclusive%20drops%20and%20rewards%20encouraged%20repeat%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20Taco%20Bell's%20digital%20strategy%2C%20Tresvant%20said%2C%20isn't%20just%20engagement%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20continue%20to%20make%20sure%20we're%20driving%20loyalty%2C%26quot%3B%20Tresvant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20PAR%20Punchh%2C%20a%20restaurant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiners-fast-food-vs-fast-casual-shake-shack-chickfila-loyalty-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eloyalty%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20software%20from%20the%20foodservice%20tech%20company%20PAR%20Technology%2C%20shows%20Gen%20Z%20surpassed%20millennials%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202024%20as%20the%20most%20active%20generation%20in%20restaurant%20loyalty%20programs.%20They%20represent%2038%25%20of%20active%20loyalty%20members%2C%20about%2035%25%20of%20check-ins%2C%20and%2049%25%20of%20new%20sign-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESavneet%20Singh%2C%20CEO%20of%20PAR%20Technology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Gen%20Z%20isn't%20just%20participating%20in%20loyalty%20programs%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20%26quot%3Bredefining%26quot%3B%20it%2C%20with%20demand%20for%20instant%20gratification%20and%20high-quality%20rewards%20for%20their%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20hoops%2C%20no%20waiting%20until%20the%20next%20visit%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20expect%20real-time%20updates%20to%20their%20loyalty%20accounts%2C%20instant%20incentives%20for%20digital%20actions%2C%20and%20perceived%20exclusivity%20like%20app-only%20items%20or%20secret%20menus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20way%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bloyalty%20powerhouse%26quot%3B%20among%20Gen%20Z%2C%20due%20to%20its%20app-only%20offers%2C%20secret%20menu%20items%2C%20pop%20culture%20collaborations%2C%20and%20gamified%20experiences%20that%20keep%20younger%20consumers%20engaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20many%20fast-food%20chains%20are%20leaning%20heavily%20on%20discounts%20to%20lure%20back%20cost-conscious%20customers%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20has%20also%20emphasized%20its%20structured%20value%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%245%2C%20%247%2C%20and%20%249%20bundle%20offerings%20%E2%80%94%20alongside%20steady%20menu%20innovation%2C%20another%20winning%20strategy%20for%20younger%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20data%20shows%20that%20millennials%20are%20the%20most%20offer-reliant%20generation%2C%20redeeming%20more%20frequently%20and%20responding%20more%20to%20discount-driven%20messaging%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20Gen%20Z%2C%20value%20extends%20beyond%20price%20to%20include%20ease%2C%20timing%2C%20and%20relevance.%20They%20want%2015%25%20off%20today%2C%20not%20a%20free%20item%20next%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Tresvant%2C%20the%20combination%20of%20Taco%20Bell's%20value%2C%20digital%20engagement%2C%20and%20cultural%20relevance%20has%20created%20a%20flywheel%20effect%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-driving-fast-food-beverage-wars-demand-custom-drinks-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyounger%20diners%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20he%20believes%20can%20hold%20up%20even%20in%20a%20volatile%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20resilient%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20Tresvant%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20brand%20that%20can%20perform%20and%20be%20successful%20in%20any%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaco-bell-gen-z-appeal-strategy-cul