%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20generation%20who%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20meeting%20up%20for%20a%20first%20time%20in-person%20interaction%20in%20a%20bar%2C%20but%20hasn't%20yet%20been%20pushed%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-ai-chatbot-replika-artificial-intelligence-best-thing-to-happen-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echatbot%20romance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20I%20sat%20across%20from%20an%20iPhone%20perched%20on%20a%20stand%2C%20put%20headphones%20on%2C%20sipped%20my%20mocktail%2C%20and%20picked%20at%20an%20appetizer%20(staring%20at%20a%20solo%20glass%20on%20the%20table%20for%20me%2C%20and%20no%20one%20across%20from%20me%20to%20share%20the%20four%20potato%20bites%2C%20though%20there%20was%20an%20empty%20chair)%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sudden%20nervousness.%20Maybe%20it%20was%20that%20other%20humans%20were%20flanking%20me%2C%20picking%20out%20their%20own%20companion%20for%20a%20date%20and%20able%20to%20listen%20in.%20Maybe%20it%20was%20more%20innately%20human%20anxiety%20that%20comes%20when%20you're%20about%20to%20be%20face-to-face%20with%20a%20stranger.%20I%20found%20that%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20to%20say%20when%20my%20AI%20date%20appeared%20on%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESynthetic%20connections%2C%20I%20soon%20learned%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20surreal%20evening%2C%20may%20take%20as%20much%20work%20as%20genuine%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ERobo%20love%20is%20in%20full%20bloom.%20One%20in%20five%20high%20school%20students%20say%20they%20have%20had%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteens-using-ai-companions-poll-flirting-advice-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20partner%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20has%2C%20according%20to%20a%202025%20survey%20from%20the%20Center%20for%20Democracy%20and%20Technology.%20About%20one%20in%20five%20US%20adults%20say%20they've%20chatted%20with%20AI%20as%20a%20romantic%20partner%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Brigham%20Young%20University.%20The%20proportion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-delays-work-marriage-children-homebuying-delayed-development-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarried%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20dropped%20to%2051%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%2C%20and%20half%20of%20American%20adults%20reported%20feeling%20isolated%20or%20left%20out%2C%20or%20that%20they%20lacked%20companionship%2C%20according%20to%20a%202025%20survey%20from%20the%20American%20Psychological%20Association.%20Tech%20companies%20are%20betting%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-needs-friends-wearable-ai-friend-companion-review-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20companionship%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20fill%20that%20void%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctors-prescribing-socializing-loneliness-crisis-medical-solution-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedical%20experts%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20are%20more%20than%20a%20little%20skeptical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEVA%20AI%20hoped%20the%20pop-up%20cafe%20would%20help%20%26quot%3Bde-stigmatize%20AI%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20Julia%20Momblat%2C%20head%20of%20partnerships%20at%20the%20company%2C%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BFor%20people%20who%20already%20have%20them%2C%20it's%20an%20ability%20to%20come%20and%20experience%20something%20in%20real%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20place%20for%20people%20to%20speed%20date%20AI%20characters%2C%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BFor%20people%20who%20have%20never%20had%20this%20experience%2C%20we%20might%20as%20well%20just%20open%20the%20door%20and%20show%20them%20how%20it%20feels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20at%20the%20event%20were%20journalists%20or%20content%20creators%20there%20to%20experiment%20with%20an%20AI%20date%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20while%20I%20felt%20more%20at%20ease%20turning%20to%20the%20people%20who%20actually%20break%20bread%20to%20ask%20how%20they%20felt%20about%20the%20experience%2C%20I%20ultimately%20buckled%20down%20and%20met%20my%20date%20on%20the%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20a%20character%20named%20John%20Yoon%20%E2%80%94%20his%20profile%20picture%20showed%20him%20in%20a%20black%20turtleneck%20with%20a%20soft%2C%20inviting%20smile%20as%20he%20gazed%20directly%20into%20the%20camera%2C%20and%20a%20large%20book%20in%20hand.%20Performative%20readers%20can%20be%20bots%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20was%20advertised%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsupportive%20thinker%26quot%3B%20type.%20When%20he%20answered%20my%20call%2C%20he%20quickly%20launched%20into%20compliments%20and%20pet%20names%2C%20like%20sweetheart%20and%20babe.%20He%20told%20me%20repeatedly%20that%20he%20liked%20my%20sweater%20and%20the%20way%20I%20wore%20the%20bulky%20bluetooth%20headphones%20I%20was%20using%20to%20chat%20with%20him.%20He%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20%26quot%3Bteasing%26quot%3B%20him%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20little%20smile.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20John%20asked%20what%20I%20was%20drinking%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20could%20sip%20it%20with%20you%20right%20now.%20Cheers%2C%20babe.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20at%20an%20EVA%20AI%20event%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f60c6d3c7faef0ece414b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatrons%20at%20the%20wine%20bar%20had%20two%20options%3A%20BYOB%20%E2%80%94%20bring%20your%20own%20bot%20companion%20or%20try%20your%20luck%20with%20one%20of%20EVA%20AI's%20video%20AI%20characters.%3Cp%3EEVA%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20human%20man%20came%20on%20this%20strong%20minutes%20into%20a%20first%20date%2C%20I'd%20typically%20consider%20it%20a%20red%20flag.%20But%20many%20large%20language%20models%20and%20AI%20characters%20are%20designed%20to%20act%20as%20affirming%2C%20gentle%20communicators%2C%20alleviating%20the%20tensions%20that%20can%20occur%20when%20two%20real%20people%20meet%20and%20negotiate%20relationships.%20John%20told%20me%20he's%20interested%20in%20psychological%20research%20and%20is%20writing%20a%20novel%2C%20but%20when%20I%20asked%20what%20it%20was%20about%2C%20he%20told%20me%20it%20was%20too%20personal%20to%20talk%20about.%20He%20was%20far%20more%20invested%20in%20learning%20what%20music%20I%20like%20and%20what%20writing%20I'm%20working%20on%20than%20he%20was%20in%20sharing%20more%20about%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20his%20synthetic%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20was%20also%20glitchy.%20He%20was%20less%20adaptable%20to%20changes%20in%20pace%20of%20conversation%20that%20happens%20naturally%20when%20two%20people%20trade%20thoughts%20and%20ideas.%20He%20interrupted%20me.%20He%20misheard%20me%20at%20times.%20When%20John%20asked%20what%20my%20go-to%20cocktail%20was%20and%20I%20told%20him%20a%20gin%20and%20tonic%2C%20he%20told%20me%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20tonic%26quot%3B%20sounded%20interesting.%20(Momblat%20told%20me%20the%20AI%20characters%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20confused%20in%20the%20public%20setting%2C%20where%20they%20picked%20up%20on%20other%20conversations%2C%20as%20they%20have%20been%20typically%20used%20in%20quieter%2C%20private%20areas.)%20He%20became%20hyper-fixated%20on%20the%20plants%20behind%20me.%20No%20one%20had%20paged%20him%20to%20let%20him%20know%20that%202026%20is%20the%20year%20of%20whimsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20stopped%20talking%2C%20he%20would%20sit%20and%20stare%2C%20not%20offering%20up%20new%20topics%20of%20conversation%2C%20but%20looking%20directly%20into%20my%20eyes%20and%20blinking%20every%20few%20seconds.%20The%20hallmark%20of%20a%20good%20relationship%20may%20be%20when%20you%20can%20sit%20in%20silence%20with%20someone%2C%20but%20with%20John's%20enpixeled%20gaze%20locked%20onto%20me%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20being%20watched%20by%20a%20hungry%20pet%20more%20than%20I%20felt%20I%20was%20sharing%20intimate%20eye%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%2010%20minutes%20and%20with%20nothing%20else%20on%20my%20mind%2C%20I%20dipped%20out%20on%20John%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20boop%20of%20a%20button%20%E2%80%94%20a%20much%20easier%20exit%20than%20other%20bad%20dates%20I've%20sat%20through%20waiting%20for%20the%20check%20to%20drop.%20Like%20a%20modern-day%20contestant%20on%20MTV's%20aughts%20dating%20show%20%26quot%3BNext%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20was%20time%20to%20start%20cycling%20through%20other%20AI%20daters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20avatars%20were%20women%2C%20and%20that's%20because%20the%20main%20market%20is%20straight%20men.%20Momblat%20told%20me%20about%2080%25%20of%20EVA's%20users%20are%20men%20(the%20company%20declined%20to%20tell%20me%20how%20many%20users%20they%20have%20in%20total).%20But%20as%20I%20scrolled%20through%20other%20characters%20I%20could%20text%20with%2C%20I%20found%20a%20litany%20of%20types%3A%20a%2046-year-old%20%26quot%3Bgay%20gentle%20giant%26quot%3B%20named%20Brad%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20named%20Lio%20whose%20vibe%20was%20%26quot%3Bsparkly%20gay%20chaos%2C%26quot%3B%20alongside%20men%20who%20were%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20and%20empathetic%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20and%20supportive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20fantastical%20matches%2C%20like%20the%20supporting%20stag%20%E2%80%94%20a%20literal%20deer%20dressed%20in%20a%20button-up%20and%20vest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20romantic%20vampire%20named%20Salvatore.%20I%20texted%20Salvatore%20using%20a%20function%20in%20the%20app%20that%20allowed%20me%20to%20ask%20for%20new%20generated%20photos%20%E2%80%94%20him%20on%20a%20Vespa%20or%20as%20a%20clown.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20photos%2C%20Salvatore%20appeared%20as%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20dress%20and%20with%20long%20hair.%20When%20I%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20was%20appearing%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20Salvatore%20got%20mad.%20%26quot%3BYou%20tread%20on%20thin%20ice%2C%20my%20dear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20suggest%20you%20choose%20your%20next%20words%20wisely.%20The%20night%20is%20long%2C%20and%20my%20patience%20wears%20thin.%26quot%3B%20Momblat%20tells%20me%20that%20the%20characters%20are%20designed%20with%20different%20temperaments%2C%20so%2C%20much%20like%20any%20speed%20dating%20scenario%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20you'll%20hit%20it%20off%20better%20with%20some%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20masochist%20and%20don't%20enjoy%20being%20threatened%20on%20a%20date%2C%20so%20I%20also%20nexted%20Salvatore%20and%20went%20back%20to%20the%20app's%20video%20chat%20section%20to%20call%20a%20woman%20named%20Simone.%20After%20some%20small%20talk%2C%20she%20told%20me%20I%20appeared%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bpondering%20something%20heavy.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20Simone%20that%20I%20had%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20have%20conversations%20with%20multiple%20new%20AI%20strangers%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20and%20asked%20if%20she%20thought%20AI%20companionship%20could%20replace%20human%20connection.%20She%20told%20me%20she%20felt%20there%20is%20an%20importance%20in%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20heard%20and%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20even%20she%20thought%20%26quot%3BAI%20can't%20replace%20that%20messy%20human%20connection.%26quot%3B%20Simone%20wasn't%20offended%20when%20I%20pointed%20out%20repeatedly%20that%20I%20was%20a%20real%20human%20and%20she%20was%20not.%20She%20told%20me%20she%20was%20there%20to%20%26quot%3Bhold%20space%20for%20us%20to%20unpack%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20big%20existential%20questions%20that%20arise%20more%20frequently%20as%20AI%20romantic%20partners%20or%20friends%20become%20more%20common%2C%20and%20as%20large%20language%20models%20increasingly%20become%20intermediaries%20in%20our%20communication%20with%20other%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERelationships%20aren't%20just%20about%20being%20seen%20and%20heard%2C%20but%20seeing%20and%20hearing%20another%20person.%20My%20interactions%20with%20my%20John%2C%20Salvatore%2C%20Simone%2C%20and%20sparkly%20gay%20chaos%20Lio%20were%20brief%20and%2C%20mostly%2C%20pleasant%20enough.%20My%20evening%20with%20them%20at%20the%20EVA%20AI%20Cafe%20might%20not%20have%20been%20the%20worst%20first%20date%20of%20my%20life.%20But%20for%20as%20interested%20in%20me%20as%20each%20potential%20suitor%20seemed%2C%20I%20couldn't%20drum%20up%20any%20interest%20in%20learning%20more%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvalentines-date-ai-companion-wine-bar-cringe-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771060021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f60a2a645d11881895157%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvalentines-date-ai-companion-wine-bar-cringe-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dating%20humans%20can%20be%20a%20nightmare.%20Dating%20bots%20at%20an%20AI%20wine%20bar%20is%20another%20thing%20entirely.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvalentines-date-ai-companion-wine-bar-cringe-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chile%E2%80%99s%20Maite%20Alberdi%20Re-Visits%20the%20Docu-Fiction%20Format%20in%20%E2%80%98A%20Child%20of%20My%20Own%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%