-lucrative-business-earnings-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBethenny%20Frankel%3C%2Fa%3E%20built%20her%20public%20persona%20in%20the%20Big%20Apple%2C%20but%20after%20moving%20to%20Florida%20in%202025%2C%20she%20says%20the%20Sunshine%20State%20is%20the%20new%20cultural%20hub%20for%20America's%20rich%20and%20famous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMiami%20is%20the%20new%20LA%2C%26quot%3B%20Frankel%2C%2055%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20way%20that%20LA%20was%20the%20cool%20place%20to%20be%2C%20and%20aspirational%20people%20wanted%20to%20be%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20March%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbethenny-frankel-supplements-diet-longevity-secrets-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20reality%20TV%20veteran%2C%20entrepreneur%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20social%20media%20influencer%20joined%20a%20wave%20of%20New%20Yorkers%20relocating%20to%20South%20Florida%2C%20settling%20on%20the%20coast%20with%20her%20teenage%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20one%20of%20many%20Americans%20leaving%20cultural%20hubs%20like%20New%20York%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20smaller%20cities%20in%20the%20Sun%20Belt.%20A%20January%202026%20Bank%20of%20America%20Institute%20study%20on%20US%20migration%20found%20that%20New%20York%20recorded%20the%20second-largest%20population%20loss%20of%20any%20US%20city%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20after%20Los%20Angeles.%20About%2045%25%20of%20outbound%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-charlotte-for-better-life-lonely-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20Yorkers%20headed%20southward%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Miami%20alone%20accounting%20for%207%25%20of%20departures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20cool%20to%20be%20in%20New%20York%2C%26quot%3B%20Frankel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20not%20as%20much%20as%20being%20in%20Miami%2C%20and%20Florida%20in%20general.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261ab3365-a8eb-4