ctivity%20has%20been%20affected%20amid%20unseasonal%20rain%20and%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20experience%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20March-May.%20This%20affects%20the%20pollination%20process%20and%20the%20harvesting%20period.%20We%20are%20small%20farmers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20good%20storage%20facilities.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20our%20harvest%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20Most%20of%20this%20produce%20gets%20wet%20in%20this%20period%20then.%20No%20cashew%20factory%20is%20ready%20to%20purchase%20this%20damaged%20product%20as%20its%20quality%20becomes%20poor%2C%20colour%20gets%20faded%2C%20and%20also%20has%20a%20poor%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2047-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20makes%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%20hotels%20in%20Kerala.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364788%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20makes%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%